# Contract: CurrentUserLight query — additive change

**File**: `src/domain/community/userCurrent/CurrentUserProvider/CurrentUserLight.graphql`
**Operation**: query `CurrentUserLight`
**Change type**: additive (no field removed, no rename)

## Diff

```diff
 query CurrentUserLight {
   me {
     user {
       ...UserDetailsLight
+      settings {
+        id
+        designVersion
+      }
       account {
         id
         authorization {
           id
           myPrivileges
         }
         license {
           id
           availableEntitlements
         }
       }
     }
   }
 }
```

